        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
          <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">Education System</h5>
              <p class="card-text">Germany's education system is known for its high standards and research-oriented approach, with many universities ranking among the world's best.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
          <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">Language</h5>
              <p class="card-text">While German is the official language, many universities offer programs taught entirely in English, especially at the postgraduate level.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
          <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">Cost of Living</h5>
              <p class="card-text">Germany offers a relatively affordable cost of living compared to other Western European countries, with various options for student accommodation.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Top Universities Section -->
  <section class="py-5">
    <div class="container">
